You can use a separate date picker and time picker and then combine the selected date with the time later. Should be very simple to do, like

DateTime date = DateTime.Today;
TimeSpan time = new TimeSpan(8, 30);

DateTime finalDateTime = date.Add(time);

You can achieve this with a little of CSS. Try to style your footer component with
```CSS
position: sticky;
    bottom: 0;
```
or
```CSS
position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
```

Currently it is only possible with custom styling only:

`<MudDrawer Class="custom-drawer">`

```
.custom-drawer .mud-drawer-content {
  height: 100%;
}
```

